snippet.title: C64 Game - Jinn Genie
snippet.description:
Fun multigenre game from 1984, released by Micromega, and coded by Hanan Samara of Dalali Software (Yogi Bear). The game doesn't have an ending so I saw how far I could get as the difficulty level gradually gets higher. 

Info: http://www.mobygames.com/game/jinn-genie-arabia-mania
Review: https://archive.org/details/commodore-user-magazine-16/page/n61/mode/2up
